{"tid":1090058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：議員詆毀香港司法制度是辜負香港","createTime":"2019-04-03T08:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T00:46:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f015e324f01b055018e53e3e355f7f19b81c46d6","tid":1090058,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2jewuUwsb9Tw0JlJFR4UIQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/L-CE-190304-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2jewuUwsb9Tw0JlJFR4UIQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FL-CE-190304-12.jpg&h=911f5a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥到立法會接受議員質詢，多名泛民議員質疑，政府修改逃犯條例帶頭破壞一國兩制。林鄭月娥重申，這次修例是為避免有人利用法例漏洞鑽空子，她又質疑有議員詆毀香港的司法制度，辜負香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅：「因為回歸要穩定人心，中共領導人亦提出一國兩制，高度自治，河水不犯井水的承諾，所以在雙方同意下，無(引渡)協議的狀態才可維持至今，這刻意的安排並非你口中所指的漏洞。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：「在今天的環境看來，它的確是一個漏洞，我會認為是有一些「空子」，讓一些人以合法的途徑避免一些他想避免的，例如逃犯被移交，因為有地理的限制或在個案移交方面，實際上是不可行，所以這次法例的修訂是希望能填塞這些空子，或堵塞漏洞，讓香港不會成為逃犯天堂。」<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸：「現在因為逃犯條例打破了中港兩地移交的防火牆，所以特首不能再迴避這關鍵的問題。你是否接受內地現在所謂的陽光司法，可以秘密扣留數年才審訊的？」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：「任何本會議員詆毀香港的司法制度，一個認為香港沒有司法獨立或者指香港有司法獨立是廢話，都是辜負了香港市民。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A9%86%E6%AF%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%BE%9C%E8%B2%A0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-035449487.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A9%2586%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25BE%259C%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-035449487.html&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5NEgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=36e3b69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A9%86%E6%AF%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6%E8%BE%9C%E8%B2%A0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-035449487.html</a>"},{"pid":"ae9690ce4025c8b7aa51fe8e35137b2bc55ca83b","tid":1090058,"uid":27451,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:01:58.000Z","msg":"奶共奶成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0312b4493dea28f239ed1d1decebf5ba271a8f2","tid":1090058,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:03:07.000Z","msg":"咁英國人做香港特首同美國人做中國國家主席又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795208f9cb8426b5b0a45bc5ed8038e0d76a4c5f","tid":1090058,"uid":26190,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"777個閪比習大大屌到爛哂流膿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276d8327ef36a2e0eb5ddca8896fb5953f9bea70","tid":1090058,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0312b4493dea28f239ed1d1decebf5ba271a8f2","tid":1090058,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:03:07.000Z","msg":"咁英國人做香港特首同美國人做中國國家主席又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"漢奸死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220b296321d03101a76400d563b390d4e70ab899","tid":1090058,"uid":102609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"都是辜負了香港市民<br />\n<br />\n你幾時代表咗香港市民<br />\n議員先係票投出嚟<br />\n你777咋 扮晒蟹咁<img src=\"/a